### ── VEHICLE SERVICE & OPERATOR PORTAL ─────────────────────────────────────
### Environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → Rest Client: Switch Environment → dev

# --- VehicleService (/vehicle) -------------------------------------------

### 1. List all vehicles — Admin
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/Vehicles
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 2. Get single vehicle — Golf VIII (seed data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/Vehicles/40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 3. Get vehicle images
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/Vehicles/40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001/images
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 4. Search vehicles — by brand and fuel type
GET {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/searchVehicles(brand='BMW',fuelType='DIESEL',transmission=null,minPrice=null,maxPrice=null,branchId=null)
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 5. Publish vehicle — DRAFT → FOR_SALE (seed vehicles are already FOR_SALE; use a newly created vehicle)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/publish
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001"
}

### 6. Archive vehicle — FOR_SALE → ARCHIVED
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/archive
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000001"
}

### 7. Add image
POST {{baseUrl}}/vehicle/addImage
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleId": "40000000-4000-4000-4000-400000000002",
  "url": "https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/BMW_3_Series_(G20).jpg",
  "sortOrder": 1
}

# --- OperatorPortalService (/operator) ------------------------------------

### 8. Create vehicle — Operator (München branch)
### EPIC20-T4: native OData CREATE (was POST /operator/createVehicle, an
### unbound action that could never be wired to a Fiori "Create" button).
### branch_ID is ignored for Operators — always forced to their own branch.
# @name createVehicle
POST {{baseUrl}}/operator/Vehicles
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vin": "WVW99999999999999",
  "plateNumber": "M OP 9999",
  "brand": "Volkswagen",
  "model": "Golf VIII 2.0 TDI",
  "year": 2023,
  "mileage": 5000,
  "fuelType": "DIESEL",
  "transmission": "AUTOMATIC",
  "color": "Blau",
  "price": 31500.00,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "branch_ID": "aaa00000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

### 9. Operator sees only their own branch vehicles
GET {{baseUrl}}/operator/Vehicles
Authorization: {{operatorAuth}}

### 10. Operator cannot see other branch vehicles — Manager sees all branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/operator/Vehicles
Authorization: {{managerAuth}}

# --- BranchService (/branch) ----------------------------------------------

### 11. List all branches
GET {{baseUrl}}/branch/Branches
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}

### 12. Get single branch — München
GET {{baseUrl}}/branch/Branches/aaa00000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Authorization: {{adminAuth}}
